					<h2>How we work?</h2>				
		<p>&nbsp;Step-by-Step with ITS Group – Building Trust, Quality, and Your Ideal Pool</p>		
					<h2>01</h2>				
					<h2>Initial Contact &amp; Inquiry
</h2>				
		<p>The client reaches out to our swimming pool construction company (ITS Group) via phone, email, or contact form. As a trusted swimming pool company, we respond promptly to understand the basic needs and schedule a one-on-one consultation.</p>		
					<h2>02</h2>				
					<h2>Site Visit &amp; Consultation
</h2>				
		<p>A technical team from our pool construction experts visits the site to assess dimensions, location, and overall feasibility. We discuss the client’s vision, preferences, budget, and the intended use of the pool — whether residential, commercial, or recreational.</p>		
					<h2>03</h2>				
					<h2>Design Proposal &amp; Concept
</h2>				
		<p>Our engineers and designers at ITS Group – a leading swimming pool company – create a tailored pool concept, including layout, materials, finishes, and unique features. 3D visualizations are available upon request for enhanced clarity.</p>		
					<h2>04</h2>				
					<h2>Technical &amp; Financial Offer
</h2>				
		<p>We submit a clear and detailed proposal covering all project phases: excavation, civil works, plumbing, waterproofing, equipment installation, tiling, lighting, and pool automation. The offer includes a transparent cost breakdown and timeline.</p>		
					<h2>05</h2>				
					<h2>Review, Revisions &amp; Agreement
</h2>				
		<p>We review the technical and financial proposal with the client, collect feedback, and revise as needed to meet expectations. Once finalized, a formal agreement is signed — marking the official start of construction with ITS Group, your trusted pool construction company.</p>		
